languages.text: "Прекрати трястись, немытый червяк, и отвечай — что это было за дерзкое нападение?"
"Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

languages.text: 「虫けらめ、震えていないで応えろ――あの非道な攻撃は一体誰の仕業だ？」
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

languages.text: “别再抖了，肮脏的臭虫！回答我，到底谁这么大的胆子，竟敢无耻地袭击我？”
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

traits.locale_text: “别再抖了，肮脏的臭虫！回答我，到底谁这么大的胆子，竟敢无耻地袭击我？”

languages.text: «Deja de temblar, gusano mugriento, y respóndeme: ¿quién se atrevería a estar detrás de un asalto tan rastrero?».
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

traits.locale_text: «Deja de temblar, gusano mugriento, y respóndeme: ¿quién se atrevería a estar detrás de un asalto tan rastrero?».

languages.text: « Cessez de trembler, vermisseau dégoûtant, et répondez-moi : qui oserait lancer une attaque aussi scandaleuse ? »
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

traits.locale_text: « Cessez de trembler, vermisseau dégoûtant, et répondez-moi : qui oserait lancer une attaque aussi scandaleuse ? »

languages.text: "Hört auf zu zittern, ungewaschener Wurm, und antwortet – wer würde einen derart unverschämten Angriff wagen?"
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

traits.locale_text: "Hört auf zu zittern, ungewaschener Wurm, und antwortet – wer würde einen derart unverschämten Angriff wagen?"

languages.text: "Titremeyi kes de cevap ver leş kokulu solucan! Böyle rezil bir saldırıya kim cüret edebilir?"
languages.original_text: "Stop quivering, unwashed worm, and answer me — who would dare to attempt such an outrageous attack?"

traits.locale_text: "Titremeyi kes seni duş almak nedir bilmez solucan! Bana yanıt ver: Böylesi ölçüsüz bir saldırıya kim teşebbüs etme cüreti gösterebilir?"
